    "description": "My Little Sister Fiona is a short kinetic novel about a brother taking care of his reclusive little sister.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAfter a traumatic experience at school, your little sister Fiona doesn't leave the house. Everyday occurrences like thunderstorms and even the mailman strike fear into her. As her older brother you do your best to make her home life as happy as possible so Fiona can smile every day. You can't imagine life without her mischief and laughter. How far will you go to make sure she feels safe and protected?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* A story about grief and moving forward after loss.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 77 character illustrations<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 20 minute reading time<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 6 Steam Achievements",
